    modified_response: "I am now creating `/src/components/ToolGateway.tsx` to showcase the Shopify Tool Gateway abstraction. This page documents the 6 mock API tools, detailing their associated parameters, scope expectations, and integration guidelines. To make it extremely high-fidelity, it features an interactive JSON Console. Selecting any tool and executing a mock call queries stateful tables from the Express server, showcasing exactly what real Shopify integrations return."
