    modified_response: "I am now creating `/src/components/ApprovalQueue.tsx` representing the SaaS Approval safeguards queue. This interface lists write actions drafted by agents (such as catalog updates or layout stylesheets customizations) which remain paused until authorized by the store owner. Clicking \"Approve\" triggers the write action to execute inside the sandbox, while rejecting logs failure and discards the buffer. Each action has an interactive code diff-viewer showing exactly what changes."
